    <div class="container">
    <h1 style="margin-left: 7.5em; margin-block-start: 2em ;"> CREATE YOUR ACCOUNT </h1><br><br>
    
         <form action="/register" method="POST">
            <div style=" width:60%; margin: 0 auto;">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="firstname"> First Name </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="First Name" id="firstName" name='firstname' required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="lastname"> Last name </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Last Name" name='lastname' id="lastname" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email"> Email-ID</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Last Name" name='email' id="email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="username"> Username </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Last Name" name='username' id="username" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password"> Password </label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Choose a strong password!" name='password' id="password" >
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="admincode"> Admin Code (For moderators only) </label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Provided to you already" name='admincode' id="admincode" >
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="avatar"> Avatar </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Profile Picture URL (optional)" name='avatar' id="avatar" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="bio"> Bio </label>
                    <textarea type="text" class="form-control"  rows=4 placeholder="About yourself"  name='description'></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Submit</button>
                <br> 
                <p style="margin: 0 auto;" class="text-center"> <a href="/campgrounds">Go Back</a> <p>
            </div>
        </form>    
</div>

<div style="margin:4em;">
    <h3> IMPORTANT NOTE: </h3>
    <ul> <h5>
    <li> Set your password such that it has more than 8 eight characters, a mix of both Upper & Lower alphabets and also symbols. </li>
    <li>Else Chome may show you a warning like "A data breach on a site or app exposed your password".</li>
    <li> The warning doesn't mean that your passwords or any other accounts got hacked. 
    <li>It means that your password isn't strong enough and it'd be safer to make it strong. <a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/thread/23534509?hl=en&msgid=23692520"> Click here </a> for more information </li>   
    <li> <strong> NOTE:</strong> Admin Code is optional and is provided to certain users who have admin access. If you haven't been provided with one, you can still signup. </li> </h5>
</div>
